title: Visio: Business Process Model and Notation (BPMN) shapes in Visio for the web [Visio Plan 2]
description:
Create BPMN-compliant processes with BPMN 2.0 shapes in Visio for the web. This feature will be available for users with a Visio Plan 2 license.
